(800000,1,'工具清单 - Overview','原文链接：https://pdai.tech/md/devops/tool/tool-list-overview.html','# 工具清单 - Overview\n\n> 工欲善其事，必先利其器，本文主要梳理下开发中可以使用的工具。@pdai\n\n## 在线工具合集 New\n\n## 清单内容\n\n- [代码托管/项目管理工具清单](https://pdai.tech/md/devops/tool/tool-list-project-management.html)\n- [看板工具清单](https://pdai.tech/md/devops/tool/tool-list-kanban.html)\n- [CI/CD工具清单](https://pdai.tech/md/devops/tool/tool-list-cicd.html)\n- [Bug管理工具清单](https://pdai.tech/md/devops/tool/tool-list-bug-tracking.html)\n- [API管理工具清单](https://pdai.tech/md/devops/tool/tool-list-api-management.html)\n- [监控工具清单](https://pdai.tech/md/devops/tool/tool-list-monitoring.html)\n- [IDE工具清单](https://pdai.tech/md/devops/tool/tool-list-ide.html)\n- [文档/Wiki/Notes管理](https://pdai.tech/md/devops/tool/tool-list-wiki-doc.html)\n- [文件管理和共享工具](https://pdai.tech/md/devops/tool/tool-list-file-management-share.html)\n\n## 参考文章\n\n- Github [awesome-selfhosted在新窗口打开](https://github.com/Kickball/awesome-selfhosted)\n- Github [awesome-sysadmin在新窗口打开](https://github.com/n1trux/awesome-sysadmin)\n\n---\n\n原文链接：https://pdai.tech/md/devops/tool/tool-list-overview.html','https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1519085360753-af0119f7cbe7?w=800','工具清单',NULL,0,NULL,'pdai-devops-tool-tool-list-overview','工具清单 - Overview - 技术博客','原文链接：https://pdai.tech/md/devops/tool/tool-list-overview.html',0,'PUBLISHED',7460,671,467,110,'2025-06-01 00:00:00','2025-06-01 00:00:00','2026-05-08 23:54:10',NULL,0) ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE `author_id`=VALUES(`author_id`),`title`=VALUES(`title`),`summary`=VALUES(`summary`),`content`=VALUES(`content`),`cover_url`=VALUES(`cover_url`),`category`=VALUES(`category`),`offline_reason`=VALUES(`offline_reason`),`featured`=VALUES(`featured`),`featured_at`=VALUES(`featured_at`),`seo_title`=VALUES(`seo_title`),`seo_description`=VALUES(`seo_description`),`warn_flag`=VALUES(`warn_flag`),`status`=VALUES(`status`),`view_count`=VALUES(`view_count`),`like_count`=VALUES(`like_count`),`favorite_count`=VALUES(`favorite_count`),`comment_count`