INSERT INTO `blog_article` (`id`,`author_id`,`title`,`summary`,`content`,`cover_url`,`category`,`offline_reason`,`featured`,`featured_at`,`slug`,`seo_title`,`seo_description`,`warn_flag`,`status`,`view_count`,`like_count`,`favorite_count`,`comment_count`,`published_at`,`created_at`,`updated_at`,`deleted_at`,`version`) VALUES
(800001,2,'工具清单 - 项目管理','原文链接：https://pdai.tech/md/devops/tool/tool-list-project-management.html','# 工具清单 - 项目管理\n\n> 来源于这里https://github.com/Kickball/awesome-selfhosted/blob/master/README.md。@pdai\n\n## 工具清单\n\n- [Bonobo Git Server在新窗口打开](https://bonobogitserver.com/) - Set up your own self hosted git server on IIS for Windows. Manage users and have full control over your repositories with a nice user friendly graphical interface. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/jakubgarfield/Bonobo-Git-Server)) `MIT` `C#`\n- [Fossil在新窗口打开](https://www.fossil-scm.org/index.html/doc/trunk/www/index.wiki) - Distributed version control system featuring wiki and bug tracker. `BSD-2-Clause-FreeBSD` `C`\n- [Goodwork在新窗口打开](https://github.com/iluminar/goodwork) - Self hosted project management and collaboration tool powered by Laravel & VueJS. ([Demo在新窗口打开](https://goodworkfor.life/)) `MIT` `PHP`\n- [Gitblit在新窗口打开](http://gitblit.com/) - Pure Java stack for managing, viewing, and serving Git repositories. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/gitblit/gitblit)) `Apache-2.0` `Java`\n- [gitbucket在新窗口打开](https://gitbucket.github.io/gitbucket-news/) - Easily installable GitHub clone powered by Scala. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/gitbucket/gitbucket)) `Apache-2.0` `Scala/Java`\n- [Gitea在新窗口打开](https://gitea.io) - Community managed fork of Gogs, lightweight code hosting solution. ([Demo在新窗口打开](https://try.gitea.io), [Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/go-gitea/gitea)) `MIT` `Go`\n- [GitLab在新窗口打开](http://gitlab.org/) - Self Hosted Git repository management, code reviews, issue tracking, activity feeds and wikis. ([Demo在新窗口打开](https://gitlab.com/), [Source Code在新窗口打开](https://gitlab.com/gitlab-org/gitlab-ce)) `MIT` `Ruby`\n- [Gitlist在新窗口打开](http://gitlist.org/) - Web-based git repository browser - GitList allows you to browse repositories using your favorite browser, viewing files under different revisions, commit history and diffs. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/klaussilveira/gitlist)) `BSD-3-Clause` `PHP`\n- [Gitolite在新窗口打开](http://gitolite.com/gitolite/index.html) - Gitolite allows you to setup git hosting on a central server, with fine-grained access control and many more powerful features. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/sitaramc/gitolite)) `GPL-2.0` `Perl`\n- [GitPrep在新窗口打开](http://gitprep.yukikimoto.com/) - Portable Github clone. ([Demo在新窗口打开](http://perlcodesample.sakura.ne.jp/gitprep/gitprep.cgi), [Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/yuki-kimoto/gitprep)) `Artistic-2.0` `Perl`\n- [Git WebUI在新窗口打开](https://github.com/alberthier/git-webui) - Standalone web based user interface for git repositories. `Apache-2.0` `Python`\n- [Gogs在新窗口打开](https://gogs.io/) - Painless self-hosted Git Service written in Go. ([Demo在新窗口打开](https://try.gogs.io/), [Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/gogits/gogs)) `MIT` `Go`\n- [Kallithea在新窗口打开](https://kallithea-scm.org/) - Source code management system that supports two leading version control systems, Mercurial and Git, with a web interface. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://kallithea-scm.org/repos/kallithea)) `GPL-3.0` `Python`\n- [Klaus在新窗口打开](https://github.com/jonashaag/klaus) - Simple, easy-to-set-up Git web viewer that Just Works. `ISC` `Python`\n- [Lavagna在新窗口打开](http://lavagna.io) - Lavagna is an open-source issue/project management tool designed for small teams. Lightweight, pure Java, easy to install, easy to use. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/digitalfondue/lavagna)) `GPL-3.0` `Java`\n- [Octobox在新窗口打开](https://octobox.io/) `⚠` - Take back control of your GitHub Notifications. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/octobox/octobox)) `AGPL-3.0` `Ruby`\n- [OpenProject在新窗口打开](https://www.openproject.org) - OpenProject is a web-based project management system. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/opf/openproject)) `GPL-3.0` `Ruby`\n- [Phabricator在新窗口打开](http://phabricator.org/) - Collection of web applications that help build better software. ([Demo在新窗口打开](https://secure.phabricator.com/), [Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/phacility/phabricator)) `Apache-2.0` `PHP`\n- [Phproject在新窗口打开](http://www.phproject.org/) - High performance full-featured project management system. ([Demo在新窗口打开](http://demo.phproject.org/), [Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/Alanaktion/phproject)) `GPL-3.0` `PHP`\n- [ProjeQtOr在新窗口打开](https://www.projeqtor.org/) - A complete, mature, multi-user project management system with extensive functionality for all phases of a project. ([Demo在新窗口打开](https://demo.projeqtor.org/), [Source Code在新窗口打开](https://sourceforge.net/p/projectorria/code/HEAD/tree/branches/)) `AGPL-3.0` `PHP`\n- [Redmine在新窗口打开](http://www.redmine.org/) - Redmine is a flexible project management web application. ([Demo在新窗口打开](http://demo.redmine.org/), [Source Code在新窗口打开](https://svn.redmine.org/redmine/)) `GPL-2.0` `Ruby`\n- [RhodeCode在新窗口打开](https://rhodecode.com/) - RhodeCode is an open source platform for software development teams. It unifies and simplifies repository management for Git, Subversion, and Mercurial. ([Demo在新窗口打开](https://try.rhodecode.com/), [Source Code在新窗口打开](https://code.rhodecode.com/)) `AGPL-3.0` `Python`\n- [SCM Manager在新窗口打开](https://www.scm-manager.org/) - The easiest way to share and manage your Git, Mercurial and Subversion repositories over http. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://bitbucket.org/sdorra/scm-manager/src)) `BSD-3-Clause` `Java`\n- [Taiga在新窗口打开](https://taiga.io/) - Agile Project Management Tool based on the Kanban and Scrum methods. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/taigaio)) `AGPL-3.0` `Python`\n- [Trac在新窗口打开](http://trac.edgewall.org/) - Trac is an enhanced wiki and issue tracking system for software development projects. `BSD-3-Clause` `Python`\n- [Tuleap在新窗口打开](https://www.tuleap.org/) - Tuleap is a libre suite to plan, track, code and collaborate on software projects. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://tuleap.net/plugins/git/tuleap/tuleap/stable?p=tuleap%2Fstable.git&a=tree)) `GPL-2.0` `PHP`\n