(800002,1,'工具清单 - IDE工具','原文链接：https://pdai.tech/md/devops/tool/tool-list-ide.html','# 工具清单 - IDE工具\n\n> 来源于这里https://github.com/Kickball/awesome-selfhosted/blob/master/README.md。@pdai\n\n## 工具清单\n\n- Babelfish - Self-hosted server for source code parsing. It can parse any file, in any supported language, extract an Abstract Syntax Tree from it, and convert it to a Universal Abstract Syntax Tree which can enable further analysis and transformation. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/bblfsh/bblfshd)) `GPL-3.0` `Go`\n- [Code-Server在新窗口打开](https://coder.com/) - Visual Studio Code in the browser, hosted on a remote server. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/cdr/code-server)) `MIT` `Nodejs/Docker`\n- [Eclipse Che在新窗口打开](http://www.eclipse.org/che/) - Open source workspace server and cloud IDE. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/eclipse/che)) `EPL-1.0` `Docker/Java`\n- [ICEcoder在新窗口打开](https://icecoder.net/) - ICEcoder is a web IDE / browser based code editor, which allows you to develop websites directly within the web browser. ([Demo在新窗口打开](http://demo.icecoder.net/ICEcoder/), [Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/icecoder/ICEcoder)) `MIT` `PHP`\n- [JS Bin在新窗口打开](http://jsbin.com/) - Open source collaborative web development debugging tool. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/jsbin/jsbin)) `MIT` `Nodejs`\n- [Judge0 API在新窗口打开](https://api.judge0.com) - Open source API to compile and run source code. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/judge0/api)) `GPL-3.0` `Ruby`\n- [Koding在新窗口打开](http://www.koding.com/) - The simplest way to manage your entire Dev Infrastructure. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/koding/koding)) `Apache-2.0` `Nodejs`\n- [Microglark在新窗口打开](http://micro.glark.io) - Hacky minimalistic remote pair programming editor. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/Bluefinch/microglark)) `AGPL-3.0` `Nodejs`\n- [Regexr在新窗口打开](http://regexr.com/) - RegExr is a HTML/JS based tool for creating, testing, and learning about Regular Expressions. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/gskinner/regexr)) `MIT` `Nodejs`\n- [RequestBin在新窗口打开](https://github.com/Runscope/requestbin) - Inspect HTTP requests. Debug webhooks. `MIT` `python`\n- [RStudio Server在新窗口打开](https://www.rstudio.com/products/rstudio/#Server) - Web browser based IDE for R. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/rstudio/rstudio)) `AGPL-3.0` `Java/C++`\n- [sourcegraph在新窗口打开](https://sourcegraph.com) - Sourcegraph is a fast, open-source, fully-featured code search and navigation engine written in Go. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/sourcegraph/sourcegraph)) `Apache-2.0` `Go`\n- [Wide在新窗口打开](https://github.com/b3log/wide) - Web-based IDE for Teams using Go programming language/Golang. ([Demo在新窗口打开](http://wide.b3log.org/signup)) `Apache-2.0` `Go`\n\n---\n\n原文链接：https://pdai.tech/md/devops/tool/tool-list-ide.html','https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1519085360753-af0119f7cbe7?w=800','工具清单',NULL,0,NULL,'pdai-devops-tool-tool-list-ide','工具清单 - IDE工具 - 技术博客','原文链接：https://pdai.tech/md/devops/tool/tool-list-ide.html',0,'PUBLISHED',2888,390,131,14,'2025-06-05 00:00:00','2025-06-05 00:00:00','2026-05-08 23:54:10',NULL,0) ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE `author_id`=VALUES(`author_id`),`title`=VALUES(`title`),`summary`=VALUES(`summary`),`content`=VALUES(`content`),`cover_url`=VALUES(`cover_url`),`category`=VALUES(`category`),`offline_reason`=VALUES(`offline_reason`),`featured`=VALUES(`featured`),`featured_at`=VALUES(`featured_at`),`seo_title`=VALUES(`seo_title`),`seo_description`=VALUES(`seo_description`),`warn_flag`=VALUES(`warn_flag`),`status`=VALUES(`status`),`view_count`=VALUES(`view_count`),`like_count`=VALUES(`like_count`),`favorite_count`=VALUES(`favorite_count`),`comment_count`=VALUES(`comment_count`),`published_at`=VALUES(`published_at`),`updated_at`=VALUES(`updated_at`),`deleted_at`=NULL;
