(800003,2,'工具清单 - 看板工具','原文链接：https://pdai.tech/md/devops/tool/tool-list-kanban.html','# 工具清单 - 看板工具\n\n> 来源于这里https://github.com/Kickball/awesome-selfhosted/blob/master/README.md。@pdai\n\n## 工具清单\n\n- [Crepido在新窗口打开](https://github.com/arshad/crepido) - Create (kanban) boards to track users and projects from flat markdown files. `MIT` `Nodejs`\n- [Kanboard在新窗口打开](http://kanboard.net/) - Simple and open source visual task board. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/kanboard/kanboard)) `MIT` `PHP`\n- [myTinyTodo在新窗口打开](http://www.mytinytodo.net/) - Simple way to manage your todo list in AJAX style. Uses PHP, jQuery, SQLite/MySQL. GTD compliant. ([Demo在新窗口打开](http://www.mytinytodo.net/demo/), [Source Code在新窗口打开](https://bitbucket.org/maxpozdeev/mytinytodo)) `GPL-2.0` `PHP`\n- [PHP Task/Todo list在新窗口打开](https://github.com/lgg/tasks.php) - Simple task/todo list that uses a JSON text file for the tasks. `MIT` `PHP`\n- [Restyaboard在新窗口打开](http://restya.com/board/) - Open source Trello-like kanban board. ([Demo在新窗口打开](http://restya.com/board/demo.html), [Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/RestyaPlatform/board)) `OSL-3.0` `PHP`\n- [scrumblr在新窗口打开](http://scrumblr.ca/) - Collaborative Online Scrum Tool Using Websockets, Node.js, jQuery, and CSS3. ([Demo在新窗口打开](http://scrumblr.ca/demo), [Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/ocdtrekkie/scrumblr/tree/sandstorm)) `GPL-3.0` `Nodejs`\n- [TaskBoard在新窗口打开](http://taskboard.matthewross.me/) - Kanban-inspired app for keeping track of things that need to get done. ([Demo在新窗口打开](https://taskboard.matthewross.me/demo.html), [Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/kiswa/TaskBoard)) `MIT` `PHP`\n- [Taskfreak在新窗口打开](http://www.taskfreak.com/original) - Simple but efficient web based task manager written in PHP. `GPL-3.0` `PHP`\n- [Tasks在新窗口打开](https://github.com/m1guelpf/tasks) - Simple tasks and notes manager written in PHP, jQuery and Bootstrap using a custom flat file database. `MPL-2.0` `PHP`\n- [Tasks在新窗口打开](https://github.com/thewhitetulip/Tasks) - Kanban based to-do list manager written in Go. `MIT` `Go`\n- [tasks.php在新窗口打开](https://github.com/RaymiiOrg/tasks.php) - Simple task/todo list manager. `MIT` `PHP`\n- [Taskwarrior在新窗口打开](https://taskwarrior.org/) - Taskwarrior is Free and Open Source Software that manages your TODO list from your command line. It is flexible, fast, efficient, and unobtrusive. It does its job then gets out of your way. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://taskwarrior.org/download/#git)) `MIT` `C++`\n- [Tinyissue在新窗口打开](https://github.com/satrun77/tinyissue) - Simple Issue Tracking for Teams. `MIT` `PHP`\n- [todo在新窗口打开](https://github.com/prologic/todo) - Simple todo list manager. ([Demo在新窗口打开](https://todo.mills.io)) `MIT` `Go`\n- [todoMini在新窗口打开](https://www.todomini.app/) - Mobile friendly zero-feature TODO list web app. Unix philosophy. ([Demo在新窗口打开](https://appmini.github.io/todoMini/?demo), [Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/appMini/todoMini)) `GPL-3.0` `PHP/Clojure`\n- [Tracks在新窗口打开](http://www.getontracks.org/) - Web-based application to help you implement David Allen’s [Getting Things Done™在新窗口打开](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Getting_Things_Done) methodology. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/TracksApp/tracks)) `GPL-2.0` `Ruby`\n- [Volition在新窗口打开](https://github.com/usevolition/volition) - Opinionated open-source task management. `MIT` `Ruby`\n- [Wekan在新窗口打开](https://wekan.github.io/) - Open-source Trello-like kanban. ([Demo在新窗口打开](https://oasis.sandstorm.io/appdemo/m86q05rdvj14yvn78ghaxynqz7u2svw6rnttptxx49g1785cdv1h), [Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/wekan/wekan)) `MIT` `Nodejs`\n\n---\n\n原文链接：https://pdai.tech/md/devops/tool/tool-list-kanban.html','https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1519085360753-af0119f7cbe7?w=800','工具清单',NULL,0,NULL,'pdai-devops-tool-tool-list-kanban','工具清单 - 看板工具 - 技术博客','原文链接：https://pdai.tech/md/devops/tool/tool-list-kanban.html',0,'PUBLISHED',3295,347,80,13,'2025-06-10 00:00:00','2025-06-10 00:00:00','2026-05-08 23:54:10'