(800004,1,'工具清单 - Bug追踪管理','原文链接：https://pdai.tech/md/devops/tool/tool-list-bug-tracking.html','# 工具清单 - Bug追踪管理\n\n> 来源于这里https://github.com/Kickball/awesome-selfhosted/blob/master/README.md。@pdai\n\n## 工具清单\n\n- [Bugzilla在新窗口打开](https://www.bugzilla.org/) - General-purpose bugtracker and testing tool originally developed and used by the Mozilla project. `MPL-2.0` `Perl`\n- [Bumpy Booby在新窗口打开](http://bumpy-booby.derivoile.fr/) - Simple, responsive and highly customizable PHP bug tracking system. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/piero-la-lune/Bumpy-Booby)) `MIT` `PHP`\n- [Cerb在新窗口打开](http://www.cerberusweb.com/) - Group-based e-mail management project. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/wgm/cerb)) `DPL` `PHP`\n- [Deskulu在新窗口打开](https://github.com/Taskulu/deskulu) - Opensource helpdesk and ticketing system based on Drupal 7. ([Demo在新窗口打开](https://help.taskulu.com)) `GPL-2.0` `PHP`\n- [DiamanteDesk在新窗口打开](http://diamantedesk.com/) - DiamanteDesk is FREE Open Source easy-to-use help-desk solution. ([Demo在新窗口打开](http://diamantedesk.com/demo/), [Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/eltrino/diamantedesk-application)) `OSL-3.0` `PHP`\n- [django-todo在新窗口打开](http://django-todo.org/) - django-todo is a pluggable, multi-user, multi-group, multi-list todo and ticketing system - a reusable app designed to be dropped into any existing Django project. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/shacker/django-todo)) `BSD-3-Clause` `Python/Django`\n- [Flyspray在新窗口打开](http://www.flyspray.org/) - Uncomplicated, web-based bug tracking system. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/Flyspray/flyspray)) `GPL-2.0` `PHP`\n- [FreeScout在新窗口打开](https://github.com/freescout-helpdesk/freescout) - Open source clone of Help Scout: email-based customer support application, help desk and shared mailbox. `AGPL-3.0` `PHP`\n- [Helpy在新窗口打开](https://helpy.io) - Helpy is a modern, open source helpdesk customer support application. Features include knowledgebase, community discussions and support tickets integrated with email. ([Demo在新窗口打开](https://demo.helpy.io), [Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/helpyio/helpy)) `MIT` `Ruby`\n- [HuBoard在新窗口打开](https://github.com/huboard/huboard) `⚠` - Instant project management for your GitHub issues (Connects directly GitHub API). `MIT` `Ruby`\n- [MantisBT在新窗口打开](https://www.mantisbt.org/) - Self hosted bug tracker, fits best for software development. ([Demo在新窗口打开](https://www.mantisbt.org/bugs/my_view_page.php)), ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/mantisbt/mantisbt)) `GPL-2.0` `PHP`\n- [OpenSupports在新窗口打开](https://www.opensupports.com/) - Multi language ticket system with FAQ, role management, metrics and canned response features. ([Demo在新窗口打开](https://www.opensupports.com/demo/), [Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/opensupports/opensupports)) `GPL-3.0` `PHP`\n- [osTicket在新窗口打开](http://osticket.com/) - Manage, organize and archive all your support requests and responses in one place. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/osTicket/osTicket)) `GPL-2.0` `PHP`\n- [OTRS在新窗口打开](http://www.otrs.com/) - Trouble ticket system for assigning tickets to incoming queries and tracking further communications. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/OTRS/otrs)) `AGPL-3.0` `Perl`\n- [Request Tracker在新窗口打开](https://www.bestpractical.com/rt/) - An enterprise-grade issue tracking system. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/bestpractical/rt)) `GPL-2.0` `Perl`\n- [Sentry On-Premise在新窗口打开](https://github.com/getsentry/onpremise) - A powerful error tracking platform with wide language support and a robust API. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/getsentry/sentry)) `BSD-3-Clause` `Python/Django`\n- [SIT在新窗口打开](https://sit.fyi/) - SCM-agnostic, file-based, offline-first, immutable issue tracker. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/sit-fyi/sit)) `MIT` `Apache-2.0` `Rust`\n- [TheBugGenie在新窗口打开](http://www.thebuggenie.org) - friendly project management and issue tracking tool, with extensive user rights system. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/thebuggenie/thebuggenie)) `MPL-2.0` `PHP`\n- [Zammad在新窗口打开](https://zammad.org/) - Easy to use but powerful open-source support and ticketing system. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/zammad/zammad)) `AGPL-3.0` `Ruby`\n\n---\n\n原文链接：https://pdai.tech/md/devops/tool/tool-list-bug-tracking.html','https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1602576666092-bf6447a729fc?w=800','工具清单',NULL,0,NULL,'pdai-devops-tool-tool-list-bug-tracking','工具清单 - Bug追踪管理 - 技术博客','原文链接：https://pdai.tech/md/devops/tool/tool-list-bug-tracking.html',0,'PUBLISHED',6623,427,501,74,'2025-06-05 00:00:00','2025-06-05 00:00:00','2026-05-08 23:54:10',NULL,0) ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE `author_id`=VALUES(`author_id`),`title`=VALUES(`title`),`summary`=VALUES(`summary`),`content`=VALUES(`content`),`cover_url`=VALUES(`cover_url`),`category`=VALUES(`category`),`offline_reason`=VALUES(`offline_reason`),`featured`=VALUES(`featured`),`featured_at`=VALUES(`featured_at`),`seo_title`=VALUES(`seo_title`),`seo_description`=VALUES(`seo_description`),`warn_flag`=VALUES(`warn_flag`),`status`=VALUES(`status`),`view_count`=VALUES(`view_count`),`like_count`=VALUES(`like_count`),`favorite_count`=VALUES(`favorite_count`),`comment_count`=VALUES(`comment_count`),`published_at`=VALUES(`published_at`),`updated_at`=VALUES(`updated_at`),`deleted_at`=NULL;
