(800005,2,'工具清单 - CI & CD','原文链接：https://pdai.tech/md/devops/tool/tool-list-cicd.html','# 工具清单 - CI & CD\n\n> 来源于这里https://github.com/n1trux/awesome-sysadmin#continuous-integration--continuous-deployment。@pdai\n\n## 工具清单\n\n- [Buildbot在新窗口打开](http://buildbot.net/) - Python-based toolkit for continuous integration. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/buildbot/buildbot)) `GPL-2.0` `Python`\n- [CapsuleCD在新窗口打开](https://analogj.github.io/capsulecd-slides/) - CD script for automating package/library releases (npm, cookbooks, gems, pip, jars, etc). ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/AnalogJ/capsulecd)) `MIT` `Go`\n- [Concourse在新窗口打开](https://concourse.ci/) - Concourse is a CI tool that treats pipelines as first class objects and containerizes every step along the way. ([Demo在新窗口打开](https://ci.concourse.ci/), [Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/concourse/concourse)) `Apache-2.0` `Go`\n- [drone在新窗口打开](https://drone.io/) - Drone is a Continuous Delivery platform built on Docker, written in Go. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/drone/drone)) `Apache-2.0` `Go`\n- [Factor在新窗口打开](http://www.factor.io/) - Programmatically define and run workflows to connect configuration management, source code management, build, continuous integration, continuous deployment and communication tools. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/factor-io/factor)) `MIT` `Ruby`\n- [GitLab CI在新窗口打开](https://about.gitlab.com/gitlab-ci/) - Gitlab\'s built-in, full-featured CI/CD solution. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://gitlab.com/gitlab-org/gitlab-ce) `MIT` `Ruby`\n- [GoCD在新窗口打开](http://www.go.cd/) - Continuous delivery server. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/gocd/gocd)) `Apache-2.0` `Java/Ruby`\n- [GolangCI在新窗口打开](https://golangci.com/) - Open Source automated code review service for Go integrated with GitHub pull requests. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/golangci/golangci)) `AGPL-3.0` `Go`\n- [Jenkins在新窗口打开](https://jenkins-ci.org/) - Continuous Integration Server. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/jenkinsci/jenkins/)) `MIT` `Java`\n- [Laminar在新窗口打开](http://laminar.ohwg.net) - Fast, lightweight, simple and flexible Continuous Integration. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/ohwgiles/laminar)) `GPL-3.0` `C++`\n- [PHP Censor在新窗口打开](https://github.com/php-censor/php-censor) - Open source self-hosted continuous integration server for PHP projects. `BSD-2-Clause` `PHP`\n- [PHPCI在新窗口打开](https://www.phptesting.org/) - Free and open source continuous integration specifically designed for PHP. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/block8/phpci)) `BSD-2-Clause` `PHP`\n- [Strider在新窗口打开](http://strider-cd.github.io/) - Open Source Continuous Deployment / Continuous Integration platform. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/Strider-CD/strider)) `MIT` `Nodejs`\n\n---\n\n原文链接：https://pdai.tech/md/devops/tool/tool-list-cicd.html','https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1585079542156-2755d9c8a094?w=800','工具清单',NULL,0,NULL,'pdai-devops-tool-tool-list-cicd','工具清单 - CI & CD - 技术博客','原文链接：https://pdai.tech/md/devops/tool/tool-list-cicd.html',0,'PUBLISHED',3259,466,47,12,'2025-06-16 00:00:00','2025-06-16 00:00:00','2026-05-08 23:54:10',NULL,0) ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE `author_id`=VALUES(`author_id`),`title`=VALUES(`title`),`summary`=VALUES(`summary`),`content`=VALUES(`content`),`cover_url`=VALUES(`cover_url`),`category`=VALUES(`category`),`offline_reason`=VALUES(`offline_reason`),`featured`=VALUES(`featured`),`featured_at`=VALUES(`featured_at`),`seo_title`=VALUES(`seo_title`),`seo_description`=VALUES(`seo_description`),`warn_flag`=VALUES(`warn_flag`),`status`=VALUES(`status`),`view_count`=VALUES(`view_count`),`like_count`=VALUES(`like_count`),`favorite_count`=VALUES(`favorite_count`),`comment_count`=VALUES(`comment_count`),`published_at`=VALUES(`published_at`),`updated_at`=VALUES(`updated_at`),`deleted_at`=NULL;
