(800006,1,'工具清单 - API管理','原文链接：https://pdai.tech/md/devops/tool/tool-list-api-management.html','# 工具清单 - API管理\n\n> 来源于这里https://github.com/Kickball/awesome-selfhosted/blob/master/README.md。@pdai\n\n## 工具清单\n\n- [DreamFactory在新窗口打开](https://www.dreamfactory.com/) - Turns any SQL/NoSQL/Structured data into Restful API. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/dreamfactorysoftware/dreamfactory)) `Apache-2.0` `PHP`\n- [Endpoint在新窗口打开](https://github.com/LINKIWI/endpoint) - Super simple mock HTTP API endpoints that return static JSON data, for testing webhooks and client libraries in development. `MIT` `Nodejs`\n- [Fusio在新窗口打开](http://www.fusio-project.org/) - Open-source API management platform which helps to build and manage REST APIs. ([Demo在新窗口打开](http://fusio-project.org/demo), [Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/apioo/fusio)) `AGPL-3.0` `PHP`\n- [Hapttic在新窗口打开](https://github.com/jsoendermann/hapttic) - Simple HTTP server that forwards all requests to a shell script to handle webhooks you receive. `Apache-2.0` `Go`\n- [Kong在新窗口打开](https://konghq.com/kong/) - The World’s Most Popular Open Source Microservice API Gateway and Platform. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/Kong/kong)) `Apache-2.0` `Lua`\n- [Para在新窗口打开](http://www.paraio.org) - Flexible and modular backend framework/server for object persistence, API development and authentication. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/erudika/para)) `Apache-2.0` `Java`\n- [Tyk在新窗口打开](https://tyk.io) - Fast and scalable open source API Gateway. Out of the box, Tyk offers an API Management Platform with an API Gateway, API Analytics, Developer Portal and API Management Dashboard. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/TykTechnologies/tyk)) `MPL-2.0` `Go`\n\n---\n\n原文链接：https://pdai.tech/md/devops/tool/tool-list-api-management.html','https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1519085360753-af0119f7cbe7?w=800','工具清单',NULL,0,NULL,'pdai-devops-tool-tool-list-api-management','工具清单 - API管理 - 技术博客','原文链接：https://pdai.tech/md/devops/tool/tool-list-api-management.html',0,'PUBLISHED',3965,402,262,17,'2025-06-19 00:00:00','2025-06-19 00:00:00','2026-05-08 23:54:10',NULL,0) ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE `author_id`=VALUES(`author_id`),`title`=VALUES(`title`),`summary`=VALUES(`summary`),`content`=VALUES(`content`),`cover_url`=VALUES(`cover_url`),`category`=VALUES(`category`),`offline_reason`=VALUES(`offline_reason`),`featured`=VALUES(`featured`),`featured_at`=VALUES(`featured_at`),`seo_title`=VALUES(`seo_title`),`seo_description`=VALUES(`seo_description`),`warn_flag`=VALUES(`warn_flag`),`status`=VALUES(`status`),`view_count`=VALUES(`view_count`),`like_count`=VALUES(`like_count`),`favorite_count`=VALUES(`favorite_count`),`comment_count`=VALUES(`comment_count`),`published_at`=VALUES(`published_at`),`updated_at`=VALUES(`updated_at`),`deleted_at`=NULL;
