(800007,2,'工具清单 - 监控工具','Monitoring software. 原文链接：https://pdai.tech/md/devops/tool/tool-list-monitoring.html','# 工具清单 - 监控工具\n\n> 来源于这里https://github.com/Kickball/awesome-selfhosted/blob/master/README.md。@pdai\n\n## 工具清单\n\n*Monitoring software.*\n\n- [Adagios在新窗口打开](http://adagios.org/) - Web based Nagios interface for configuration and monitoring (replacement to the standard interface), and a REST interface, [SourceCode在新窗口打开](https://github.com/opinkerfi/adagios), [Documentation在新窗口打开](https://github.com/opinkerfi/adagios/wiki))\n- [Alerta在新窗口打开](https://github.com/guardian/alerta) - Distributed, scaleable and flexible monitoring system.\n- [Bloonix在新窗口打开](https://bloonix.org) - Bloonix is a monitoring solution that helps businesses to ensure high availability and performance. `GPLv3` `Perl`\n- [bolo在新窗口打开](http://bolo.niftylogic.com/) - A Do-it-Yourself monitoring framework built to gather metrics, mine data and report on the systems in your network.\n- [Bosun在新窗口打开](http://bosun.org/) - Monitoring and alerting system by Stack Exchange ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/bosun-monitor/bosun), [Documentation在新窗口打开](http://bosun.org/quickstart.html)) `MIT` `Go`\n- [Cacti在新窗口打开](http://www.cacti.net) - Web-based network monitoring and graphing tool.\n- [Cabot在新窗口打开](http://cabotapp.com/) - Monitoring and alerts, similar to PagerDuty.\n- [cadvisor在新窗口打开](https://github.com/google/cadvisor) - Analyzes resource usage and performance characteristics of running containers ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/google/cadvisor)) `Apache` `Go`\n- [check_mk在新窗口打开](http://mathias-kettner.com/check_mk.html) - Collection of extensions for Nagios.\n- [Dash在新窗口打开](https://github.com/afaqurk/linux-dash) - A low-overhead monitoring web dashboard for a GNU/Linux machine.\n- [EdMon在新窗口打开](https://github.com/Edraens/EdMon) - A command-line monitoring application helping you to check that your hosts and services are available, with notifications support. `MIT` `Java`\n- [ElastiFlow在新窗口打开](https://github.com/robcowart/elastiflow) - Network flow Monitoring (Netflow, sFlow and IPFIX) with the Elastic Stack.\n- [eZ Server Monitor在新窗口打开](http://www.ezservermonitor.com) - A lightweight and simple dashboard monitor for Linux, available in Web and Bash application.\n- [Flapjack在新窗口打开](http://flapjack.io/) - Monitoring notification routing & event processing system.\n- [Healthchecks在新窗口打开](https://healthchecks.io/) - Monitoring for cron jobs, background services and scheduled tasks.\n- [Icinga在新窗口打开](https://www.icinga.org/) - Nagios fork that has since lapped nagios several times. Comes with the possibility of clustered monitoring - ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/Icinga)) - `GPLv2`\n- [LibreNMS在新窗口打开](http://www.librenms.org) - Fully featured network monitoring system that provides a wealth of features and device support.\n- [Monit在新窗口打开](http://mmonit.com/monit/#home) - Small utility for managing and monitoring Unix systems.\n- [Munin在新窗口打开](http://munin-monitoring.org/) - Networked resource monitoring tool.\n- [Naemon在新窗口打开](http://www.naemon.org/) - Network monitoring tool based on the Nagios 4 core with performance enhancements and new features.\n- [Nagios在新窗口打开](https://www.nagios.org/) - Computer system, network and infrastructure monitoring software application.\n- [NetXMS在新窗口打开](https://www.netxms.org/) - Open Source network and infrastructure monitoring and management. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/netxms/netxms))\n- [Observium在新窗口打开](http://www.observium.org/) - SNMP monitoring for servers and networking devices. Runs on linux.\n- [OMD在新窗口打开](http://omdistro.org/) - The Open Monitoring Distribution.\n- [Performance Co-Pilot在新窗口打开](http://pcp.io) - Lightweight, distributed system performance and analysis framework.\n- [PhpSysInfo在新窗口打开](https://phpsysinfo.github.io/phpsysinfo/) - A customizable PHP script that displays information about your system nicely.\n- [PHP Server Monitor在新窗口打开](https://www.phpservermonitor.org/) - Open source tool to monitor your servers and websites\n- [psdash在新窗口打开](https://github.com/Jahaja/psdash) - A linux system information web dashboard using psut ils and flask.\n- [pyDash在新窗口打开](https://k3oni.github.io/pydash/) - Small web-based monitoring dashboard for linux.\n- [Riemann在新窗口打开](http://riemann.io/) - Flexible and fast events processor allowing complex events/metrics analysis.\n- [rtop在新窗口打开](https://github.com/rapidloop/rtop) - an interactive, remote system monitoring tool based on SSH.\n- [Sensu在新窗口打开](https://sensuapp.org/) - Monitoring framework.\n- [ServerStatus BotoX在新窗口打开](https://github.com/BotoX/ServerStatus) - Display and monitor your servers statistics in a beatiful way.\n- [ServerStatus moejda在新窗口打开](https://github.com/mojeda/ServerStatus) - Server Status website script, displays uptime (days), free RAM, free HDD\n- [Shinken在新窗口打开](http://www.shinken-monitoring.org/) - Another monitoring framework.\n- [SWMP - Server Web Monitor Page在新窗口打开](https://swmp.ml/) - A responsive, eye-pleasing Linux server statistics dashboard.([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/fuzzymannerz/swmp))\n- [Thruk在新窗口打开](http://www.thruk.org/) - Multibackend monitoring web interface with support for Naemon, Nagios, Icinga and Shinken.\n- [Uchiwa在新窗口打开](https://uchiwa.io/) - Simple dashboard for sensu.\n- [Vector在新窗口打开](https://github.com/Netflix/vector/) - An on-host performance monitoring framework.\n- [Xymon在新窗口打开](https://www.xymon.com/) - Network monitoring inspired by Big Brother.\n- [Zabbix在新窗口打开](http://www.zabbix.com/) - Enterprise-class software for monitoring of networks and applications.\n- [Zenoss在新窗口打开](http://community.zenoss.org) - Application, server, and network management platform based on Zope.\n\n---\n\n原文链接：https://pdai.tech/md/devops/tool/tool-list-monitoring.html','https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1585079542156-2755d9c8a094?w=800','工具清单',NULL,0,NULL,'pdai-devops-tool-tool-list-monitoring','工具清单 - 监控工具 - 技术博客','Monitoring software. 原文链接：https://pdai.tech/md/devops/tool/tool-list-monitoring.html',0,'PUBLISHED',5788,472,138,6,'2025-06-22 00:00:00','2025-06-22 00:00:00','2026-05-08 23:54:10',NULL,0) ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE `author_id`=VALUES(`author_id`),`title`=VALUES(`title`),`summary`=VALUES(`summary`),`content`=VALUES(`content`),`cover_url`=VALUES(`cover_url`),`category`=VALUES(`category`),`offline_reason`=VALUES(`offline_reason`),`featured`=VALUES(`featured`),`featured_at`=VALUES(`featured_at`),`seo_title`=VALUES(`seo_title`),`seo_description`=VALUES(`seo_description`),`warn_flag`=VALUES(`warn_flag`),`status`=VALUES(`status`),`view_count`=VALUES(`view_count`),`like_count`=VALUES(`like_count`),`favorite_count`=VALUES(`favorite_count`),`comment_count`=VALUES(`comment_count`),`published_at`=VALUES(`published_at`),`updated_at`=VALUES(`updated_at`),`deleted_at`=NULL;
