(800008,1,'工具清单 - 文档/Wiki/Notes','Useful Wikis for Sysadmins – not to be confused with Wiki software. 原文链接：https://pdai.tech/md/devops/tool/tool-list-wiki-doc.html','# 工具清单 - 文档/Wiki/Notes\n\n> 来源于这里https://github.com/Kickball/awesome-selfhosted/blob/master/README.md。@pdai\n\n## 工具清单\n\n*Useful Wikis for Sysadmins – not to be confused with Wiki software.*\n\n- [ArchWiki在新窗口打开](https://wiki.archlinux.org/) – Arch Linux Wiki which has really nice written articles valid for other distros.\n- [Gentoo Wiki在新窗口打开](https://wiki.gentoo.org/) - Gentoo Linux Wiki with a lot in-detail description of Linux components.\n\n- [BookStack在新窗口打开](https://www.bookstackapp.com/) - BookStack is a simple, self-hosted, easy-to-use platform for organizing and storing information. It allows for documentation to be stored in a book like fashion. ([Demo在新窗口打开](https://www.bookstackapp.com/#demo), [Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/ssddanbrown/BookStack)) `MIT` `PHP`\n- [Cowyo在新窗口打开](https://github.com/schollz/cowyo) - Cowyo is a feature-rich wiki for minimalists. ([Demo在新窗口打开](https://cowyo.com)) `MIT` `Go`\n- [django-wiki在新窗口打开](https://github.com/django-wiki/django-wiki) - Wiki system with complex functionality for simple integration and a superb interface. Store your knowledge with style: Use django models. ([Demo在新窗口打开](https://demo.django-wiki.org/)) `GPL-3.0` `Python`\n- [Documize在新窗口打开](https://documize.com) - Modern Docs + Wiki software with built-in workflow, single binary executable, just bring MySQL/Percona. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/documize/community)) `AGPL-3.0` `Go`\n- [Dokuwiki在新窗口打开](https://www.dokuwiki.org/DokuWiki) - Easy to use, lightweight, standards-compliant wiki engine with a simple syntax allowing reading the data outside the wiki. All data is stored in plain files, therefore no database is required. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/splitbrain/dokuwiki)) `GPL-2.0` `PHP`\n- [Gitit在新窗口打开](https://github.com/jgm/gitit) - Wiki program that stores pages and uploaded files in a git repository, which can then be modified using the VCS command line tools or the wiki\'s web interface. `GPL-2.0` `Haskell`\n- [Gollum在新窗口打开](https://github.com/gollum/gollum) - Simple, Git-powered wiki with a sweet API and local frontend. `MIT` `Ruby`\n- [jingo在新窗口打开](https://github.com/claudioc/jingo) - Git based wiki engine written for node.js, with a decent design, a search capability and good typography. ([Demo在新窗口打开](http://jingo.cica.li:6067/wiki/home)) `MIT` `Nodejs`\n- [Mediawiki在新窗口打开](https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/MediaWiki) - MediaWiki is a free and open-source wiki software package written in PHP. It serves as the platform for Wikipedia and the other Wikimedia projects, used by hundreds of millions of people each month. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://phabricator.wikimedia.org/diffusion/MW/)) `GPL-2.0` `PHP`\n- [MoinMoin在新窗口打开](https://moinmo.in/) - Advanced, easy to use and extensible WikiEngine with a large community of users. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](http://hg.moinmo.in/moin)) `GPL-2.0` `Python`\n- [Olelo在新窗口打开](https://github.com/minad/olelo) - Olelo is a wiki that stores pages in a Git repository, supports many markup styles and has an extensible, hackable architecture. ([Demo在新窗口打开](http://gitwiki.org/)) `MIT` `Ruby`\n- [Outline在新窗口打开](https://www.getoutline.com/) `⚠` - An open, extensible, wiki for your team built using React and Node.js. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/outline/outline)) `BSD-3-Clause` `Nodejs`\n- [Pepperminty Wiki在新窗口打开](https://github.com/sbrl/Pepperminty-Wiki) - Complete markdown-powered wiki contained in a single PHP file. ([Demo在新窗口打开](https://starbeamrainbowlabs.com/labs/peppermint/build/)) `MPL-2.0` `PHP`\n- [PineDocs在新窗口打开](https://github.com/xy2z/PineDocs) - Simple, fast, customizable and lightweight site for browsing files. `GPL-3.0` `PHP`\n- [PmWiki在新窗口打开](http://www.pmwiki.org) - Wiki-based system for collaborative creation and maintenance of websites. `GPL-3.0` `PHP`\n- [Raneto在新窗口打开](http://raneto.com/) - Raneto is an open source Knowledgebase platform that uses static Markdown files to power your Knowledgebase. `MIT` `Nodejs`\n- [Realms在新窗口打开](http://realms.io/) - Git-backed wiki inspired by Gollum. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/scragg0x/realms-wiki)) `GPL-2.0` `Python`\n- [TiddlyWiki在新窗口打开](http://tiddlywiki.com/) - Reusable non-linear personal web notebook. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/Jermolene/TiddlyWiki5)) `BSD-3-Clause` `Nodejs`\n- [Tiki在新窗口打开](https://tiki.org) - Wiki CMS Groupware with the most built-in features. ([Demo在新窗口打开](https://tiki.org/Demo), [Source Code在新窗口打开](https://sourceforge.net/p/tikiwiki/code/HEAD/tree/)) `LGPL-2.1` `PHP`\n- [TWiki在新窗口打开](http://twiki.org/) - TWiki is a Perl-based structured wiki application, typically used to run a collaboration platform, knowledge or document management system, a knowledge base, or team portal. ([Demo在新窗口打开](http://twiki.org/cgi-bin/view/Sandbox/WebHome), [Source Code在新窗口打开](http://svn.twiki.org/svn/twiki/)) `GPL-1.0` `Perl`\n- [wiki在新窗口打开](https://github.com/prologic/wiki) - Simple Markdown based wiki engine. ([Demo在新窗口打开](https://wiki.mills.io)) `MIT` `Go`\n- [Wiki.js在新窗口打开](https://wiki.js.org/) - Modern, lightweight and powerful wiki app built on NodeJS, Git and Markdown. ([Demo在新窗口打开](https://docs.requarks.io)) `AGPL-3.0` `Nodejs`\n- [WiKiss在新窗口打开](http://wikiss.tuxfamily.org/) - Wiki, simple to use and install. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://svnweb.tuxfamily.org/listing.php?repname=wikiss/svn&path=%2F&sc=0)) `GPL-2.0` `PHP`\n- [XWiki在新窗口打开](http://www.xwiki.org) - Second generation wiki that allows the user to extend its functionalities with a powerful extension-based architecture. ([Demo在新窗口打开](http://playground.xwiki.org), [Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/xwiki/xwiki-platform)) `LGPL-2.1` `Java`\n- [Docstore在新窗口打开](http://haldean.org/) - Static document hosting without any server-side processing, does not require you to recompile every time you change an article. Clone the repository and add articles in the text/ directory to get started. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/haldean/docstore)) `BSD-3-Clause` `Javascript`\n- [Flatdoc在新窗口打开](http://ricostacruz.com/flatdoc/) - Small Javascript file that fetches Markdown files and renders them as full pages. `MIT` `Javascript`\n- [markdown-tree在新窗口打开](https://github.com/mil/markdown-tree) - Serve a hierarchy / tree directory of markdown files. Use intended for small sites built in markdown. `MIT` `Ruby`\n- [Read the Docs在新窗口打开](https://docs.readthedocs.org/en/latest/install.html) - Host documentation, making it fully searchable and easy to find; import your docs using any major version control system, including Mercurial, Git, Subversion, and Bazaar. ([Demo在新窗口打开](https://readthedocs.org/projects/), [Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/rtfd/readthedocs.org)) `MIT` `Python`\n\n- https://www.staticgen.com\n\n---\n\n原文链接：https://pdai.tech/md/devops/tool/tool-list-wiki-doc.html','https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1519085360753-af0119f7cbe7?w=800','工具清单',NULL,0,NULL,'pdai-devops-tool-tool-list-wiki-doc','工具清单 - 文档/Wiki/Notes - 技术博客','Useful Wikis for Sysadmins – not to be confused with Wiki software. 原文链接：https://pdai.tech/md/devops/tool/tool-list-wiki...',0,'PUBLISHED',7862,433,516,150,'2025-06-25 00:00:00','2025-06-25 00:00:00','2026-05-08 23:54:10',NULL,0) ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE `author_id`=VALUES(`author_id`),`title`=VALUES(`title`),`summary`=VALUES(`summary`),`content`=VALUES(`content`),`cover_url`=VALUES(`cover_url`),`category`=VALUES(`category`),`offline_reason`=VALUES(`offline_reason`),`featured`=VALUES(`featured`),`featured_at`=VALUES(`featured_at`),`seo_title`=VALUES(`seo_title`),`seo_description`=VALUES(`seo_description`),`warn_flag`=VALUES(`warn_flag`),`status`=VALUES(`status`),`view_count`=VALUES(`view_count`),`like_count`=VALUES(`like_count`),`favorite_count`=VALUES(`favorite_count`),`comment_count`=VALUES(`comment_count`),`published_at`=VALUES(`published_at`),`updated_at`=VALUES(`updated_at`),`deleted_at`=NULL;
