(800009,2,'工具清单 - 文件管理和共享','原文链接：https://pdai.tech/md/devops/tool/tool-list-file-management-share.html','# 工具清单 - 文件管理和共享\n\n> 来源于这里https://github.com/Kickball/awesome-selfhosted/blob/master/README.md。@pdai\n\n## 工具清单\n\n- [Git Annex在新窗口打开](https://git-annex.branchable.com/) - File synchronization between computers, servers, external drives. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://git.joeyh.name/index.cgi/git-annex.git/)) `GPL-3.0` `Haskell`\n- [Kinto在新窗口打开](https://kinto.readthedocs.org) - Kinto is a minimalist JSON storage service with synchronisation and sharing abilities. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/Kinto)) `Apache-2.0` `Python`\n- [Nextcloud在新窗口打开](https://nextcloud.com/) - Access and share your files, calendars, contacts, mail and [more在新窗口打开](https://apps.nextcloud.com/) from any device, on your terms. ([Demo在新窗口打开](https://demo.nextcloud.com/), [Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/nextcloud/server)) `AGPL-3.0` `PHP`\n- [OpenSSH/SFTP在新窗口打开](http://www.openssh.com/) - Secure File Transfer Program. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](http://cvsweb.openbsd.org/cgi-bin/cvsweb/src/usr.bin/ssh)) `BSD-2-Clause` `C`\n- [ownCloud在新窗口打开](https://owncloud.org/) - All-in-one solution for saving, synchronizing, viewing, editing and sharing files, calendars, address books and more. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/owncloud/core), [Clients在新窗口打开](https://github.com/owncloud/core/wiki/Apps)) `AGPL-3.0` `PHP`\n- [Pydio在新窗口打开](https://pydio.com/) - Turn any web server into a powerful file management system and an alternative to mainstream cloud storage providers. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/pydio/pydio-core)) `AGPL-3.0` `PHP`\n- [Samba在新窗口打开](https://www.samba.org/) - Samba is the standard Windows interoperability suite of programs for Linux and Unix. It provides secure, stable and fast file and print services for all clients using the SMB/CIFS protocol. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://git.samba.org/samba.git/)) `GPL-3.0` `C`\n- [Seafile在新窗口打开](https://www.seafile.com/en/home/) - File hosting and sharing solution primary for teams and organizations. ([Demo在新窗口打开](https://seacloud.cc/demo), [Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/haiwen/seafile)) `GPL-2.0` `C`\n- [SparkleShare在新窗口打开](http://sparkleshare.org/) - Self hosted, instant, secure file sync. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/hbons/SparkleShare)) `GPL-3.0` `C#`\n- [Syncany在新窗口打开](https://www.syncany.org/) - Secure file sync software for arbitrary storage backends, an open-source cloud storage and filesharing application. Securely synchronize your files to any kind of storage. `GPL-3.0` `Java`\n- [Syncthing在新窗口打开](https://syncthing.net/) - Syncthing is an open source peer-to-peer file synchronisation tool. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://github.com/syncthing/syncthing)) `MPL-2.0` `Go`\n- [Unison在新窗口打开](https://www.cis.upenn.edu/~bcpierce/unison/) - Unison is a file-synchronization tool for OSX, Unix, and Windows. `GPL-3.0` `OCaml`\n- [Z-Push在新窗口打开](http://z-push.org/) - Implementation of Microsoft’s [ActiveSync在新窗口打开](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ActiveSync) protocol. ([Source Code在新窗口打开](https://stash.z-hub.io/projects/ZP/repos/z-push)) `AGPL-3.0` `PHP`\n\n---\n\n原文链接：https://pdai.tech/md/devops/tool/tool-list-file-management-share.html','https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1585079542156-2755d9c8a094?w=800','工具清单',NULL,0,NULL,'pdai-devops-tool-tool-list-file-management-share','工具清单 - 文件管理和共享 - 技术博客','原文链接：https://pdai.tech/md/devops/tool/tool-list-file-management-share.html',0,'PUBLISHED',6243,455,358,116,'2025-06-28 00:00:00','2025-06-28 00:00:00','2026-05-08 23:54:10',NULL,0) ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE `author_id`=VALUES(`author_id`),`title`=VALUES(`title`),`summary`=VALUES(`summary`),`content`=VALUES(`content`),`cover_url`=VALUES(`cover_url`),`category`=VALUES(`category`),`offline_reason`=VALUES(`offline_reason`),`featured`=VALUES(`featured`),`featured_at`=VALUES(`featured_at`),`seo_title`=VALUES(`seo_title`),`seo_description`=VALUES(`seo_description`),`warn_flag`=VALUES(`war